    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>When a creature spills your blood, you can use your magic to strike back.</em></p><p>You can use this ability when a creature hits you with a melee attack while you are @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.W6yKtk7Svvy9dIq9]{Raging}. You target the creature who damaged you.</p><p><strong>When Hit by a Weapon Attack</strong> - 1 Creature (10 ft.) - Magical</p><p><strong>Dexterity Save</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 1d6 force]] damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success</strong>: Half damage.</p></li></ul><p>​</p><p><em>Because this ability only works once per turn, a creature that hits you multiple times only takes this damage once.</em></p>",
      "chat": "<p>You can use this ability when a creature hits you with a melee attack while you are @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.W6yKtk7Svvy9dIq9]{Raging}. You target the creature who damaged you.</p><p><strong>Reaction</strong> - 1 Creature (15 ft.) - Magical</p><p><strong>Dexterity Save</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 1d6 force]] damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success</strong>: Half damage.</p></li></ul>"
